No, I didn't.Remember that night

26:45.212 --> 26:47.910
on the submarine?

26:47.954 --> 26:50.434
When we dressed up
as Victoria's Secret Angels?

26:50.478 --> 26:52.219
In Liverpool?

26:52.262 --> 26:53.612
Madagascar.

26:53.655 --> 26:55.178
You were in the
Giselle sequin wings,

26:55.222 --> 26:58.007
I was in the Naomi feathers.

27:00.314 --> 27:02.621
You were drunk and
insecure about us.

27:02.664 --> 27:05.362
And I said I'd prove
my love to you

27:05.406 --> 27:07.538
by giving you everything I had?

27:07.582 --> 27:09.105
I gave you...

27:09.149 --> 27:11.542
all of my accounts.

27:11.586 --> 27:13.849
You signed the documents,
putting everything in your name.

27:13.893 --> 27:15.938
Oh, my God, I do remember.

27:18.506 --> 27:20.639
I signed the papers
and then that man that said

27:20.682 --> 27:22.292
that he works for
Paul Manafort came on board

27:22.336 --> 27:24.120
and took everything.Exactly.

27:24.164 --> 27:26.035
And after Michael
started sniffing around,

27:26.079 --> 27:28.124
I had to do something
to stop him, didn't I?

27:28.168 --> 27:29.560
So you...

27:29.604 --> 27:31.388
Would do anything
to protect you?

27:31.432 --> 27:33.782
Even though you're the
reason I'm in prison?

27:33.826 --> 27:35.871
Yes.

27:37.177 --> 27:39.222
Why are you trying
to claw your way

27:39.266 --> 27:41.703
back into Rafael's life
when you have someone

27:41.747 --> 27:43.313
who loves you?

27:43.357 --> 27:45.533
Unconditionally.

27:45.576 --> 27:47.361
I even sent someone
to watch over you.

27:48.449 --> 27:49.842
"Girl"?

27:49.885 --> 27:51.800
Girl. Girl. Girl.

27:51.844 --> 27:53.976
Go to him, Luisa.

27:54.020 --> 27:56.587
Then I'll know you love me, too.

27:59.765 --> 28:02.115
That will never happen.

28:03.725 --> 28:05.727
We'll see.

28:14.388 --> 28:17.565
Listen up,
everyone, focus.

28:17.608 --> 28:20.002
I assure you we are
addressing our oxygen shortage.

28:20.046 --> 28:22.613
Our Martian filters
will deliver

28:22.657 --> 28:24.615
breathable air
very soon.

28:24.659 --> 28:26.835
Yes, you.

28:26.879 --> 28:28.184
Mr. President,
what about the rumored affair

28:28.228 --> 28:30.447
with your interplanetary
ambassador?

28:30.491 --> 28:34.190
For the last time,
my relationship with Blooki

28:34.234 --> 28:36.192
is strictly professional.

28:36.236 --> 28:38.760
REPORTER:
So you deny the rumors?

28:38.804 --> 28:41.197
She doesn't even
have a mouth.

28:43.939 --> 28:45.288
What about the milkshake?

28:48.204 --> 28:49.292
I'm gonna have a baby?

28:49.336 --> 28:50.641
MATEO:
Yes, me, Mommy.

28:50.685 --> 28:52.818
Mom? Mommy.
What about me?

28:52.861 --> 28:53.993
I can't focus.

28:54.036 --> 28:55.603
Mommy, Mommy. Mommy!

28:55.646 --> 28:57.605
ALL :
Mommy, Mommy, Mommy...

28:57.648 --> 28:59.912
Oh, boy.

28:59.955 --> 29:01.783
Is it a bad time?

29:01.827 --> 29:04.394
Nope. Actually,
I can use a break.

29:04.438 --> 29:06.570
But don't worry,
I'll get Dina the pages.

29:06.614 --> 29:08.572
Actually, that's
why I'm here.

29:08.616 --> 29:10.183
Uh...

29:10.226 --> 29:12.707
I spoke to
your mother...

29:12.751 --> 29:14.753
and I want to let
you off the hook.

29:14.796 --> 29:17.016
What do you mean?Well, you can quit
the telenovela

29:17.059 --> 29:18.757
if you'd rather
be writing your novel.

29:18.800 --> 29:20.759
No, no. I-I'm just
feeling overwhelmed.

29:20.802 --> 29:22.456
There's a lot going on
right now.

29:22.499 --> 29:24.893
You won't hurt my feelings
if you don't want to do it.

29:24.937 --> 29:26.895
Thanks, Dad.

29:26.939 --> 29:29.289
But it's also a lot of money.

29:29.332 --> 29:32.727
Well, being paid
to make art is tricky.

29:32.771 --> 29:34.729
Money can buy a lot of things.

29:34.773 --> 29:36.426
But passion isn't one of them.

29:36.470 --> 29:38.733
You have to follow
your passion.

29:38.777 --> 29:40.604
And, frankly, I need

29:40.648 --> 29:43.390
someone who will live
and breathe the telenovela.

29:43.433 --> 29:45.261
Because this is my passion.

29:45.305 --> 29:47.873
My novel has been calling to me.

29:47.916 --> 29:50.440
Then answer the muse.
Dina will write the show.

29:50.484 --> 29:52.051
But she won't even speak to you.

29:52.094 --> 29:54.444
Let me worry about that.
You get your book done.

29:54.488 --> 29:56.751
PETRA:
Oh, thank God.

29:56.795 --> 29:58.666
I missed you so much.
Mmm.

29:58.709 --> 30:01.234
It's just been
a few days.
Mmm.

30:01.277 --> 30:03.497
I know, but I missed you
every minute of those days.

30:03.540 --> 30:05.847
Mmm.

30:05.891 --> 30:08.284
So?
Drumroll.

30:08.328 --> 30:10.112
LATIN LOVER NARRATOR:
On it.

30:10.156 --> 30:12.114
They offered me the job.

30:12.158 --> 30:13.507
Really?

30:13.550 --> 30:15.465
Congratulations.
Wait.

30:15.509 --> 30:16.945
That's not even
the biggest news.

30:16.989 --> 30:18.468
I got another job offer

30:18.512 --> 30:20.644
on the way back
from the airport.

30:20.688 --> 30:23.604
From the Florida
Immigrant Commission.

30:23.647 --> 30:25.171
Oh, that's great news.

30:25.214 --> 30:26.694
They don't even want
to interview me.

30:26.737 --> 30:29.697
They said I came
so highly recommended.

30:29.740 --> 30:31.830
Yes.

30:31.873 --> 30:34.658
By one of their biggest donors.

30:34.702 --> 30:37.139
Wait, you did this?

30:37.183 --> 30:38.793
I sit on the board

30:38.837 --> 30:41.491
of several charitable
organizations in Miami.

30:41.535 --> 30:43.319
When I learned
you were interested
in immigration policy,

30:43.363 --> 30:45.887
I put out feelers for any
similar opportunities here.

30:45.931 --> 30:48.847
Without asking me first?

30:48.890 --> 30:50.283
I thought you'd be happy.

30:50.326 --> 30:51.850
You don't have
to move to Houston.

30:51.893 --> 30:53.286
We don't have
to do long distance.

30:53.329 --> 30:55.897
I can't believe
you did that.

30:55.941 --> 30:57.333
There was a problem,
and I solved it.

30:57.377 --> 30:58.987
Wh-What's the issue?

30:59.031 --> 31:01.685
The issue is I want a
girlfriend, not a headhunter.

31:01.729 --> 31:04.514
Don't you think you've
done enough for my career?

31:04.558 --> 31:06.386
I was only trying to help.After what happened

31:06.429 --> 31:09.432
last time, your help is...

31:09.476 --> 31:10.999
the last thing I need.

31:14.960 --> 31:16.439
I know there's a lot
of anxiety for parents

31:16.483 --> 31:17.876
around this
whole process,

31:17.919 --> 31:19.529
so I'll cut
to the chase.

31:19.573 --> 31:21.836
I believe Mateo does have ADHD.

31:25.753 --> 31:27.276
I w...

31:27.320 --> 31:30.323
What does that mean
for him, specifically?

31:30.366 --> 31:32.542
Well, Mateo really struggles
with both inattention

31:32.586 --> 31:33.848
and impulsivity.

31:33.892 --> 31:35.241
His executive functions

31:35.284 --> 31:36.938
are somewhat impaired,
which is why

31:36.982 --> 31:40.942
tasks aren't completed, why he
has trouble self-regulating.

31:42.552 --> 31:44.554
It's just harder
for Mateo to focus

31:44.598 --> 31:46.861
and prioritize
than it is for other kids.

31:46.905 --> 31:48.515
How can we help him?

31:48.558 --> 31:50.038
Well, there are
treatment options that range

31:50.082 --> 31:52.780
from behavior interventions
to medication.

31:52.823 --> 31:54.651
I'm happy to go over
all of that with you.

31:54.695 --> 31:56.175
Thank you.

31:57.828 --> 32:00.135
Sorry, I...

32:00.179 --> 32:03.269
just trying to imagine
what it feels like for Mateo.

32:03.312 --> 32:06.011
LATIN LOVER NARRATOR:
You know what? Let me show you
what it feels like.

32:06.054 --> 32:07.926
Oh, wait, look at that.

32:07.969 --> 32:10.232
Whoops. Spoiler alert.

32:10.276 --> 32:11.755
Oh, hello, Alba.

32:11.799 --> 32:13.757
Ooh, pretty bug.

32:13.801 --> 32:16.325
Now, where were we?

32:20.112 --> 32:24.072
You okay?Yeah. Fine.

32:24.116 --> 32:25.595
Oh, come on.

32:25.639 --> 32:28.903
You were the strong one
for me yesterday.

32:28.947 --> 32:31.384
I promise I'm good,
so if you need to fall apart

32:31.427 --> 32:34.082
a little... I'm here.

32:34.126 --> 32:38.086
I'm just scared.

32:38.130 --> 32:40.436
And a little sad.

32:40.480 --> 32:42.612
Yeah, I know.

32:42.656 --> 32:46.965
I just want him
to have a good life.He will.

32:47.008 --> 32:48.923
I don't want it
to be harder.

32:48.967 --> 32:50.055
It might be.Oh...

32:50.098 --> 32:52.971
But, hey, that's
all he knows.

32:53.014 --> 32:56.235
I just keep thinking
about something

32:56.278 --> 32:58.367
a friend of mine said.

32:58.411 --> 33:01.501
How Mateo's the same great kid
today as he was yesterday.

33:07.072 --> 33:08.987
That friend sounds
super smart.

33:09.030 --> 33:11.641
She can be.

33:11.685 --> 33:15.689
We've got this.
Together.

33:23.349 --> 33:25.046
All right, I'm going to win Dina
over with this super-sized

33:25.090 --> 33:27.918
cupcake I made.
What do you think?

33:29.529 --> 33:30.834
Isn't that just a cake?

33:30.878 --> 33:33.359
It's-- oh.

33:33.402 --> 33:34.838
No baked goods,

33:34.882 --> 33:36.927
Rogelio, that won't help.

33:36.971 --> 33:38.929
Hey.

33:38.973 --> 33:40.235
Hey.

33:40.279 --> 33:42.020
You doing okay?

33:42.063 --> 33:43.847
How are you feeling about Mateo?

33:43.891 --> 33:47.895
Uh, I'm still processing,
but okay.

33:47.938 --> 33:49.157
Good.

33:49.201 --> 33:50.680
And you and Rafael?

33:50.724 --> 33:52.900
Also better.

33:52.943 --> 33:55.729
But we are adjusting
our custody agreement.

33:56.599 --> 33:57.557
It's kind of like

33:57.600 --> 33:58.558
homeowner's insurance.

33:58.601 --> 34:00.038
You get it when things are good

34:00.081 --> 34:01.604
to protect when things aren't.

34:03.215 --> 34:04.390
I think that's smart.

34:04.433 --> 34:07.567
And I also think
you look sad.

34:07.610 --> 34:09.569
I just don't want to prepare
for a future

34:09.612 --> 34:12.224
where Rafael and I
aren't together.

34:12.267 --> 34:15.444
But it's like Mateo's diagnosis.

34:15.488 --> 34:18.665
I don't like it, it's hard,
but I have to accept it.

34:18.708 --> 34:21.363
Relationships change,
people change.

34:21.407 --> 34:25.106
Yes. That's so true.

34:26.499 --> 34:28.066
And you know what?

34:28.109 --> 34:31.156
That's exactly why I don't need
this giant cupcake.

34:33.984 --> 34:36.726
I mean, I would
have had some.

34:38.859 --> 34:40.730
Oh.

34:43.298 --> 34:46.693
I was very clear. I will only
speak to you through Jane.

34:46.736 --> 34:49.435
I know. And that's actually
what I'm here about.

34:49.478 --> 34:51.698
Jane is no longer
working on this project.

34:51.741 --> 34:55.049
Therefore, is no longer
available to act as our buffer.

34:55.093 --> 34:56.442
Then I'm off the project.

34:56.485 --> 34:57.660
Please, Dina.

34:57.704 --> 35:00.054
I don't trust anyone else
to get it right.

35:00.098 --> 35:01.795
You were there
from the beginning,

35:01.838 --> 35:03.971
and you're the only one
who has the passion for it.

35:04.014 --> 35:05.277
Well, you should have
thought about that

35:05.320 --> 35:06.930
one of the numerous times
you so egregiously

35:06.974 --> 35:08.584
mistreated and disrespected me!

35:08.628 --> 35:11.935
You're right. I was a selfish
and inconsiderate man.

35:11.979 --> 35:14.199
But I've changed since
we last worked together.

35:14.242 --> 35:16.070
Why should I believe that?

35:16.114 --> 35:17.637
I thought you
might ask that,

35:17.680 --> 35:19.595
which is why it's not my word
I'm asking you to believe.

35:19.639 --> 35:21.119
It's theirs.

35:26.776 --> 35:27.995
I have also

35:28.038 --> 35:30.258
egregiously mistreated
and disrespected

35:30.302 --> 35:31.781
each of these women.

35:31.825 --> 35:34.175
He abandoned me for his career.

35:34.219 --> 35:37.657
He broke his contract
and ruined my reality show.

35:37.700 --> 35:39.137
He burned off my eyebrows,

35:39.180 --> 35:40.312
got my toe bitten off by a wolf,

35:40.355 --> 35:42.401
and paralyzed half my face.

35:42.444 --> 35:44.229
Oh, my God.

35:44.272 --> 35:46.013
LATIN LOVER NARRATOR:
Geez, how is this guy
still standing?

35:46.056 --> 35:49.234
And yet they have
all forgiven me.

35:49.277 --> 35:50.583
I had a baby with him.

35:50.626 --> 35:52.411
I married him.

35:52.454 --> 35:55.153
I signed on to spend
the next seven to ten years

35:55.196 --> 35:56.937
of my life with him.

35:56.980 --> 35:58.765
And they did that because
I've grown and changed.

35:58.808 --> 36:01.420
Sort of.
A little.

36:01.463 --> 36:02.986
His heart's in the right place.

36:03.030 --> 36:04.988
ROGELIO:
Dina, I promise,

36:05.032 --> 36:06.860
if you decide to work with me
on this pilot,

36:06.903 --> 36:08.731
I will not repeat the mistakes
of the past.

36:08.775 --> 36:10.472
And because you have

36:10.516 --> 36:13.301
zero reason to believe the
words coming out of my mouth,

36:13.345 --> 36:16.957
I've even put it
in writing.

36:17.000 --> 36:19.351
I've made us a contract.
For insurance.

36:19.394 --> 36:21.527
So we have
rules in place

36:21.570 --> 36:23.181
in case things go bad.

36:23.224 --> 36:26.009
And these three women
are your guarantee

36:26.053 --> 36:27.489
that it
will be enforced.

36:27.533 --> 36:29.230
One toe out of line,

36:29.274 --> 36:31.058
and I will have these three
in my ear.

36:31.101 --> 36:33.495
I mean, seriously, like...

36:36.629 --> 36:37.891
...from every direction.

36:37.934 --> 36:38.935
Shut it, Rogelio!

36:42.722 --> 36:44.202
Okay.

36:44.245 --> 36:46.204
Yougot a deal.

36:46.247 --> 36:47.596
Thank you.

36:47.640 --> 36:49.511
Thank you, thank you,
thank you.

36:49.555 --> 36:51.078
You won't regret this.

36:51.121 --> 36:53.123
To Mars we go.

36:54.473 --> 36:55.952
LATIN LOVER NARRATOR:
Oh, sorry.

36:55.996 --> 36:57.345
Lost focus for a second.

36:57.389 --> 36:58.651
Here we are.

36:58.694 --> 37:00.566
I didn't mean to overstep.

37:00.609 --> 37:02.263
I love you.

37:02.307 --> 37:05.048
I would never do anything
to undermine your happiness.

37:05.092 --> 37:06.963
I know I overreacted.

37:07.007 --> 37:09.444
Yeah, you were just
trying to help.

37:09.488 --> 37:12.360
Honestly, I think
I was just...

37:12.404 --> 37:15.711
looking for a fight.

37:15.755 --> 37:17.365
Why?

37:17.409 --> 37:19.062
Thing is...

37:19.106 --> 37:21.891
spending time in Houston
made me realize

37:21.935 --> 37:25.721
how much I need
a fresh start.

37:25.765 --> 37:28.681
Nobody there
knows my history

37:28.724 --> 37:31.074
or looks at me like
I'm a criminal or...

37:31.118 --> 37:32.728
a bartender.

37:32.772 --> 37:34.252
Really...

37:34.295 --> 37:36.689
the idea of starting over

37:36.732 --> 37:39.866
is even more appealing
than the job itself.

37:39.909 --> 37:41.259
Oh.

37:41.302 --> 37:43.043
I am so sorry.

37:43.086 --> 37:45.480
No. I get it.

37:45.524 --> 37:48.004
I understand the need
for a fresh start.

37:48.048 --> 37:50.180
We'll just...

37:50.224 --> 37:52.922
make long distance work.

37:52.966 --> 37:55.316
Patti's been begging me
for a comeback.

37:55.360 --> 37:59.277
No, I mean a...
complete fresh start.

38:00.713 --> 38:02.410
Being away for a few days

38:02.454 --> 38:04.107
helped me understand...

38:04.151 --> 38:06.588
that it's impossible
for me to look at you

38:06.632 --> 38:08.808
without seeing all
of our baggage.

38:08.851 --> 38:11.114
I've forgiven you,
but I want to put

38:11.158 --> 38:13.378
the trauma of this
past year behind me.

38:15.075 --> 38:17.991
And I can't do that
with you in my life.

38:18.034 --> 38:20.167
What?

38:20.210 --> 38:21.951
No.

38:21.995 --> 38:23.605
I'm so sorry.

38:23.649 --> 38:27.957
But I... need
to start over.

38:28.001 --> 38:31.657
LATIN LOVER NARRATOR:
And as Petra's heart broke
into a million pieces,

38:31.700 --> 38:33.311
Jane was finally able

38:33.354 --> 38:35.791
to put the pieces
of her novel together.

38:35.835 --> 38:38.620
See, as soon as she cleared the distractions from her mind,

38:38.664 --> 38:41.623
her executive functions
began to, well...

38:41.667 --> 38:44.322
really function.

38:44.365 --> 38:45.453
Jane, I need to talk to you.

38:45.497 --> 38:47.455
I need you to lock
your front door.

38:47.499 --> 38:50.023
LATIN LOVER NARRATOR:
Oh, looks like Jane
included Petra in the novel.

38:50.066 --> 38:51.372
Jane!

38:51.416 --> 38:52.982
Oh, my bad.

38:53.026 --> 38:54.070
What's wrong? S-Sit.

38:56.203 --> 38:58.814
Can I use this rag?

38:58.858 --> 39:01.643
Well, that's my sweatshirt...

39:01.687 --> 39:05.343
J.R.'s taking the
job in Houston

39:05.386 --> 39:07.432
and she broke up with me,

39:07.475 --> 39:11.000
and I feel like someone cut
out a piece of my heart.

39:11.044 --> 39:12.828
Oh, Petra.

39:12.872 --> 39:14.308
I'm fine. I should go.

39:14.352 --> 39:16.179
I just thought
you'd want to know.

39:16.223 --> 39:18.268
Sit your butt back down here.

39:18.312 --> 39:20.401
You're not
going anywhere.

39:20.445 --> 39:23.926
Okay. Can I sleep
here tonight?

39:23.970 --> 39:25.972
Of course.
Just give me a second.

39:33.109 --> 39:36.417
You want to hear
something really stupid?

39:38.637 --> 39:41.248
I-I was gonna propose.

39:41.291 --> 39:43.424
Oh, no.

39:43.468 --> 39:45.644
Hey, it could be
a friendship ring.

39:45.687 --> 39:47.994
Ah, it's already engraved.

39:48.037 --> 39:49.909
"Petra and Jane."

39:53.216 --> 39:55.654
Thank you for letting
me stay here.

39:55.697 --> 39:58.352
That's what sisters are for.

39:58.396 --> 39:59.832
LATIN LOVER NARRATOR:
Aw.

39:59.875 --> 40:02.748
If only our story
could end there.

40:02.791 --> 40:05.664
But this is a telenovela
after all.

40:05.707 --> 40:07.448
Luisa, you have
to stop calling me.

40:07.492 --> 40:10.973
I just needed to tell you
something important.

40:11.017 --> 40:15.064
I did sign my name
to Rose's accounts.

40:15.108 --> 40:16.457
I knew it.

40:16.501 --> 40:18.067
You are such a liar.

40:18.111 --> 40:20.940
No, I wasn't lying.
I just didn't remember doing it.

40:20.983 --> 40:23.595
It was years ago when I was...
I was blackout drunk.

40:23.638 --> 40:25.466
Oh, of course.But I am not...

40:25.510 --> 40:27.729
still working with Rose.

40:27.773 --> 40:29.514
I promise.Luisa.

40:29.557 --> 40:31.646
Enough. I'm done.

40:31.690 --> 40:34.519
Don't come near me
or my family again.

40:41.526 --> 40:43.136
Hey, girl, what's up?

40:43.179 --> 40:44.442
I'm in.

40:44.485 --> 40:46.792
What does Rose need me to do?

40:48.141 --> 40:49.229
LATIN LOVER NARRATOR:
Oh, boy.

40:49.272 --> 40:50.970
I don't want to focus on that.

